metadata.description: The new Reptikas Smart Contract has been deployed, new address 0x6C3C15ECDd6A0C3b92C8Ed6113d3d5A6338aa3Ca. If you had participated in our Gift Mint or won an NFT on the old contract, you have already been airdropped a 1:1 token from the new contract. I.E. if you owned token 30 on the old contract, you have been airdropped token 30 from the new contract.
